The paper also addresses the issue of pipeline optimization, which is related to data science and data analysis, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper discusses the integration of Pareto optimization, which is a technique used in software engineering and optimization, making cs.SE (Software Engineering) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the practical applications of the tool, which could fall under the category of computational engineering, making cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) a possible sub-category.
